data.description: Welcome home. This is a solid brick ranch home, tucked away on the edge of the woods for privacy but still within a short distance to all the amenities of downtown Crete. The curb appeal that comes along with the updated landscaping is the one of many things that brings this home to life. The home offers a newly installed wireless doorbell system, a freshly painted main floor, with a large breakfast bar that opens into our large but cozy family room highlighted by our beautiful brick fireplace. There is beautiful hardwood flooring that runs from the living room, to the family room, and into the bedrooms. The master suite hosts 1 of 3 full bathrooms that this home has to offer. The amount of storage that this home has to offer from top to bottom is outstanding. The fully finished basement has plenty of space for additional bedrooms or office space. The basement also hosts a built in bar and full bathroom which makes it perfect for indoor entertaining. For the outdoor entertaining, enjoy a solid deck that overlooks your fenced in spacious backyard that makes it perfect for BBQ's, parties, and bon fires. This home also has a large attached, heated, 2 car garage (with a brand new garage door) that has a floor drain w/attached water spout for making car washing a breeze. This home is move in ready and awaiting on you. Bring in the holidays with comfort. Property is being sold As-Is.
